# Backend Standards

## Allowed Scope
- `functions/**`
- `firebase.json` when backend configuration changes are requested

## Forbidden Scope
- `src/**`
- Runtime UI implementation files

## Priorities
- Keep business logic in `functions/src/**`.
- Validate payloads and auth assumptions explicitly.
- Avoid silent failures; return/log explicit errors.
- Keep notification/event processing deterministic and testable.

## Boundary Enforcement
- Do not implement UI changes from backend tasks.
- If frontend updates are required, hand off to `frontend-gemschi`.
